    "More recently, deep learning methods have provided significant improvements in performance terms in multiple visual analysis tasks, such as object detection, classification and tracking.",
    "Deep learning models typically contain hundreds of thousands or even millions of trainable parameters, which give them their edge in terms of performance [133].",
    "Finally, the goal of clustering is to discover the natural groupings of a set of objects.",
    "Many clustering algorithms are generic in the sense that they can be applied to any type of data that are equipped with a measure of distance between data points.",
